    </div><p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">The above mentioned difference did not appear due
    to different interests, it was caused by the conditions which affect the state of things.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">As far as the attitude and motivation of country
    population for sport are concerned, the following was found on the sample of 3650 subjects</font></p>
