    </div><p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">Differences in attitudes and interests are not due
    to smaller wishes, but to the degree of possibility to satisfy peoples needs in their free
    time.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">Negative influences of the speed of changes in life
    nowadays are present in the rural areas as well. This is way these people also need
    recreative compensation of biological character. Without healthy, strong, persistent, fast
    and agile country people we cannot expect good life neither in the country nor in towns,
    although they might have modern agricultural technical devices.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">A person learns and creates in sport, but he/she should
    also be able to enjoy it. We believe in the logical and progressive sequence
    WORK-FAMILY-ORDER-RECREATION everywhere, both in the country and in the cities, all over
    the world.</font></p>
    <b><p ALIGN="CENTER"><font size="2">REFERENCES</font></p>
    </b><p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">1. Ostojic, S. Stanje i problemi rekreactje
    potjoprivrednika. FFK, Beograd.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">2. Central fizicke kulture Vojvodine, Novi Sad VVV</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">3. Zivanovic, Z. Narodni viseboj Beograd </font></td>
